FT  18 AUG 94 / World Commodities Prices: Cotton
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Liverpool - Spot and shipment sales amounted to 193 tonnes for the week
ended 12 August against 290 tonnes in the previous week. Subdued offtake did
not bring many operations. Support was forthcoming in certain specialist
styles notably in the Central Asian range. American growths made some
headway.
