<HEADLINE>
FT  17 AUG 94 / World News in Brief: British soldier killed in Bosnia
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A British soldier was killed in central Bosnia while on a mine clearance
operation. Sapper Barry John Nicholas, 20, from Dagenham, Essex, was the
eighth British soldier to die in the region since troops were sent there in
1992. Serbs fire from UN arms zone, Page 2
